{"id":22,"date":"2023-03-10T01:21:31","date_gmt":"2023-03-10T01:21:31","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost\/BSU-Open%20University\/?page_id=22"},"modified":"2023-04-03T16:20:04","modified_gmt":"2023-04-03T08:20:04","slug":"admission-requirements","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/admission-requirements\/","title":{"rendered":"Admission"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">There are crucial deadlines to remember whether you&#8217;re contemplating applying, have already filed your application, or have already received an offer of admission to BSU-OU. Learn which dates in this part of your journey you need to be on the lookout for. <em><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/events\/\">Check it Here<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n<p><i class=\"fa-solid fa-shoe-prints\"><\/i><b style=\"color:Red; font-size:16px\"> APPLICATION STEPS<b><\/b><\/b><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:100\">For your&nbsp;<strong>INITIAL APPLICATION<\/strong>&nbsp;we only accept scanned copies of original documents or self-uploaded digital copies. <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/submission\/\">submit online here<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>If you receive an&nbsp;<strong>ADMISSION OFFER<\/strong>, you will have to provide hard copies thru secure electronic delivery or post mail of academic documents.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<p><i class=\"fa-regular fa-file-lines\"><\/i><b style=\"color:Red; font-size:16px\"> HOW TO SUBMIT OFFICIAL ACADEMIC DOCUMENTS<b><\/b><\/b><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be considered official, academic records must either be received in person at the university office or be received via&nbsp;secure electronic delivery or post mail &nbsp;from the issuing institution.<\/p>\n\n\n<p><i class=\"fa-solid fa-check\"><\/i><b style=\"color:Red; font-size:16px\"> REQUIRED DOCUMENTS<b><\/b><\/b><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">1. Certified Photocopy of Official Transcript of Records with Remarks <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">\u201c<em>Issued for BSU<\/em>\u201d<\/span><\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">2. Certificate of Transfer Credential from the school that you last attended.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">3. Two letters of recommendation from your former professors\/employer&nbsp;(for degree program).<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">4. Four copies of your latest identical ID picture (2\u201d x 2\u201d) with plain white background.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">5. Permit to Study from the head of your agency if employed.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">6. Payment of Application Fee of PhP100 for Filipinos and US$25 for foreign nationals (Non-refundable).<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">7. An essay of about 500 words indicating your purpose for applying to the distance education program and your plan after completing the degree.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">8. Photocopy of PSA birth certificate and marriage certificate (if married)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">9. Valid Visa for foreign nationals.<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-2\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:43px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-1-Application-for-Admission-1-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-1-Application-for-Admission-1-1.pdf\">OU Form 1 Application for Admission<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-2-Recommendation-Form-1-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-2-Recommendation-Form-1-1.pdf\">OU Form 2 Recommendation Form<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-3-Permit-to-Study-1-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/OU-Form-3-Permit-to-Study-1-1.pdf\">OU Form 3 Permit to Study<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-horizontal is-content-justification-left is-layout-flex wp-container-4\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/BSU-Open%20University\/index.php\/contact-us\/\">Contact Us<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>There are crucial deadlines to remember whether you&#8217;re contemplating applying, have already filed your application, or have already received an&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_price":"","_stock":"","_tribe_ticket_header":"","_tribe_default_ticket_provider":"","_tribe_ticket_capacity":"0","_ticket_start_date":"","_ticket_end_date":"","_tribe_ticket_show_description":"","_tribe_ticket_show_not_going":false,"_tribe_ticket_use_global_stock":"","_tribe_ticket_global_